From: bluecat <lmhtq1991@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2026 21:30:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Phase C-1: StoplessGC HotSpot skeleton

Adds src/hotspot/share/gc/stopless/ — the new CollectedHeap subclass
for the CHERI-Stopless GC. v1 implementations are minimum-viable
stubs: TLAB disabled, alloc returns nullptr (caller throws OOM),
collect is a no-op. Real behaviour comes in C-3 (arena) and C-9
(concurrent mover).

Files:
- stoplessArguments.hpp/.cpp   — GCArguments subclass
- stoplessBarrierSet.hpp/.cpp  — BarrierSet (read=NOP, write=NOP)
- stoplessHeap.hpp/.cpp        — CollectedHeap with all 17u pure
                                 virtuals stubbed
- stopless_globals.hpp         — product flag declarations
- vmStructs_stopless.hpp       — empty placeholder

Design: docs/c1/design.md
Overview: docs/17_phase_c_overview.md

